➜张柏芝说过的“芝言骗语”，已经足够出一本书了吧？
http://www.sohu.com/a/317287654_407929	30833
<p class="ql-align-justify">最新一期天天向上里，张柏芝和大张伟相遇，然后微博热搜上立马出现了#大张伟追问张柏芝#的名场面。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">事情是这样的，汪涵问大家喜不喜欢粤菜，最喜欢的是哪一道。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/afd45a85a0e943d987c279a114572bb3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">张柏芝说自己从小喜欢做菜，儿子喜欢的菜都是自己做的。大儿子喜欢中餐，二儿子就喜欢西餐。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">（？？？这和汪涵的问题有什么关系？）</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/bc8e8238399047f7943fb11dfb986ba5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">接着大张伟灵魂发问：“分别喜欢什么菜？”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/a0556de5071c41b3b1817367f9c51122.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>张柏芝以为大张伟在应和她于是说：“对我每天都要做两个不一样的菜。”</p>
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/a28e45c0eb1f498a8bbb840b1bb6cd52.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>大张伟紧追不舍：“那分别喜欢吃什么菜？”</p>
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/d87b5c73a8bc4f30b42978d4517cbe33.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">张柏芝回答：“你说哪一个儿子？第三个喜欢奶。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/ae300d102f194506a18f8cf54579d012.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">留下大张伟一脸懵逼：一定是我问问题的方式不对。深吸一口气接着问：</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/ff9fc61f215141e68a10672dc6eca4fd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">张柏芝一脸听不懂的样子，钱枫出来解围了：“你为什么一定要知道？”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/9ca68553ace34b0c8b365262db812823.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>张柏芝还是一句话不说，于是李湘出来圆场了：“他小朋友，十万个为什么。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/8d09b8e203f74c58890b19b17d3d53ee.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">大张伟持续发问。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/8fe8614e8b3a471fa8feab9872aaa32e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">张柏芝回答，一个喜欢中餐一个喜欢西餐，她自己喜欢蔬菜。（这里有转移注意力的嫌疑！）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/899cbbc74a2a406486ea094a35570b5d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">大张伟调整问法：“什么菜？菜名。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/801df647017a48e3b939cc40a9f81f91.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">张柏芝一个恍然大悟的表情，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/61862b5c620a4fb2a1562ed2f9b196a7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">想了想然后说一个喜欢白米饭，一个喜欢汉堡包。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/e7ffe5a7e8a5444c95b8f9c5c218425f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">果然啊一个中餐一个西餐。大老师终于歇了一口气。没想到这时候张柏芝又说：“我从小就只喜欢吃素，我从来没吃过肉。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/d18870518ced4bd4bc52b33f836be240.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>汪涵钱枫两脸懵逼。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/8440e3f73e3148af998ba2a22bb14dbc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>李湘说很疑惑说：“其实小时候爸爸妈妈给你吃你也不知道啊。”张柏芝一脸惊恐说：“我妈妈打我到不行。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/64944167bf5241f4974c89ddb8a9294a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>感情你从没吃过肉你就知道你不喜欢肉而且从来不吃？</p>
<p>感情你做饭摆拍发微博就完了自己不吃？</p>
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/8c0fb558b83140349894707724995f91.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">感情排骨在你眼中不是肉？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/cb78ae8ea16348fa8bc4574f15074602.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">锅包肉也不是肉？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/a4bf8e912a8140afb40a1e5738025395.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">当然了，张柏芝撒谎翻车的现场也不只一次。她的“芝言骗语”真的可以出一本书。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">比如说自己是长不胖的体质，而且每天都要吃夜宵，不吃睡不着，越吃越瘦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/91969ab2c59b44689b633af079e29c24.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">然后又说生了孩子之后每天只吃一个鸡蛋来减肥。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/107bd6b54b63458f89aecd64aa3b851a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/a59f4d969dd749408839b2ee2f89ae9f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/2b21dfd8db8743ffb44ca60361d68b60.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">？？？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">您不是吃不胖长不胖吗？？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">例如直接在节目里说自己是最年轻金像奖影后，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/ad80ed2e30d147059971808a6b376392.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">那一脸我其实觉得没什么但没办法大家就觉得我牛逼的表情让我差点就信了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/c52d45fad81a4312bb540803ccebcf30.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">再例如上内地节目带人参观自己的豪宅，显示自己满是书籍的房间。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/1f5715ec02aa4516b9f7b6360ea46517.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">指着一堆画说那全是她儿子画的。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/360d1e709dac48938b1909bb56a2b7c8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/312c39f723414e60b5bd83a5fb74cb71.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">后来被港媒爆出张柏芝的“豪宅”装潢和好几部港剧里的相同，被质疑是戏剧样品屋。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/c93320162edb4ac3976a24c70960ce2b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">再后来又被爆出张柏芝儿子的画。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">大儿子的。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/5103261884bd46cab70d10a58f33da0f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">小儿子的。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/18b40513de8c444a9c1e74d35c4c1910.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有一次说自己连续三个月每天开工，工作人员都要给她下安眠药来让她睡觉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/56d87c6d453445fc985b38ce42adce23.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">又有一次说自己连续睡觉十六天不醒来。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/41b527db179c41bba2b22113eb02966c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">但这是正常现象，家人都见怪不怪了还会帮她敷面膜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/0b495486232640a18604498f14cf5b4f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/b817aafe97c6423bb0750e61fb2369b9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有张柏芝对于自己的时间安排也是“自律”的吓人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/186664fb473846339b4adc5e1726292a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">每天五到八个小时的运动。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还要，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">帮儿子补习四小时的数学……</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/6acf66d0adf741d88498cf3df7995393.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">提问：补数学这种脑力活动算不算在五到八个小时的运动时间之内？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">翻完这一本《芝言骗语》，看着一代玉女现在满嘴跑火车我真的不知道该生气还是惋惜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/7c3a115d68b349d8855dd7f6598790b8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">有的谎话，我觉得只要是一个正常的成年人都说不出口，那假的有点好笑了吧？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">但是张柏芝还是说了，说了一次两次，还有三次四次，让我都忍不住去怀疑，她是不是经历了什么所以心里有一些……创伤？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">所以才会把这些话像骗小孩一样当着全国观众说出来？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不过这也只有她自己知道了，我们吃瓜群众还是老老实实的啃颜吧。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190529/592311ead84840bd81c86a599bb448f4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>